HELP XT_NEW_SCROLLED_TEXT                               Steve Knight, Oct 93
                                                        SIREN Project

    xt_new_scrolled_text( PARENT, [NAME], BINDING1, ..., BINDINGn )
        -> WIDGET

This procedure creates a new Motif text widget that is contained inside
a ScrolledWindow using -XmCreateScrolledText-.  The arguments are processed
using *XT_NEW_ARGS.

The menu bar widget returned by this function is automatically managed.

See also:
    HELP *XT_NEW_ARGS
